	<description><![CDATA[
	<p align="justify"><strong>IOS Newsletter</strong> is a newsletter component and mailing list manager for Elxis CMS
   created by <strong>Ioannis Sannos</strong> 
   (<a href="http://www.isopensource.com" title="isopensource.com" target="_blank">Is Open Source</a>) and released for 
   <strong>free</strong> 
	under the <a href="http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/3.0/" title="Creative Commons 3.0" target="_blank">
	Creative Commons Attribution-Noncommercial-Share Alike 3.0</a> license.<br /><br />
  On <strong>version 1.1</strong> IOS Newsletter SEO PRO base prefix, used to generate the short URLs, changed from 
  <em>com_newsletter</em> to <em>newsletter</em>. The shorter URLs work only on Elxis 2009.0 or newer. IOS Newsletter 
  1.1 will work fine on Elxis 2008.x but using the old <em>com_newsletter</em> SEO PRO base prefix. IOS Newsletter 
  detects automatically your Elxis version and sets the proper SEO PRO base prefix. Version 1.2 is also compatible 
  with PHP 5.3.<br /><br />For support visit <a href="http://forum.elxis.org" title="Elxis forum" target="_blank">Elxis forum</a>.<br /><br />
  <strong>version 1.3</strong> Some fixes for Elxis 2009.2.</p>
	]]>
